{"data":[{"name":"111:1","price":"1. அழியட்டும் அபூலஹபின் இரு கரங்கள்; அவனுமே அழியட்டும்!","arabic":"تَبَّتۡ يَدَآ أَبِي لَهَبٖ وَتَبَّ","category":["111 (Al-Masad)","Al-Masad","Surah Al-Masad"],"ayahNumber":6217,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"tabbat yadā abī lahabin watabba ","translations":["Perish","(the) hands","(of) Abu","Lahab","and perish he","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["tabbat","yadā","abī","lahabin","watabba",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,830],[2,830,3270],[3,3270,3910],[4,3910,5620],[5,5620,6805]]}},{"name":"111:2","price":"2. அவனுடைய பொருளும், அவன் சேகரித்து வைத்திருப்பவைகளும் அவனுக்கு ஒரு பயனுமளிக்காது.","arabic":"مَآ أَغۡنَىٰ عَنۡهُ مَالُهُۥ وَمَا كَسَبَ","category":["111 (Al-Masad)","Al-Masad","Surah Al-Masad"],"ayahNumber":6218,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"mā aghnā ʿanhu māluhu wamā kasaba ","translations":["Not","(will) avail","him","his wealth","and what","he earned","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["mā","aghnā","ʿanhu","māluhu","wamā","kasaba",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2380],[2,2380,3040],[3,3040,3860],[4,3860,5010],[5,5010,5450],[6,5450,6305]]}},{"name":"111:3","price":"3. வெகு விரைவில் அவன் கொழுந்துவிட்டெரியும் நெருப்பில் நுழைவான்.","arabic":"سَيَصۡلَىٰ نَارٗا ذَاتَ لَهَبٖ","category":["111 (Al-Masad)","Al-Masad","Surah Al-Masad"],"ayahNumber":6219,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"sayaṣlā nāran dhāta lahabin ","translations":["He will be burnt","(in) a Fire","of","Blazing Flames","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["sayaṣlā","nāran","dhāta","lahabin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,2760],[3,2760,3610],[4,3610,4885]]}},{"name":"111:4","price":"4. விறகு சுமக்கும் அவனுடைய மனைவியோ,","arabic":"وَٱمۡرَأَتُهُۥ حَمَّالَةَ ٱلۡحَطَبِ","category":["111 (Al-Masad)","Al-Masad","Surah Al-Masad"],"ayahNumber":6220,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-im'ra-atuhu ḥammālata al-ḥaṭabi ","translations":["And his wife","(the) carrier","(of) firewood","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-im'ra-atuhu","ḥammālata","al-ḥaṭabi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1520],[2,1520,3880],[3,3880,4805]]}},{"name":"111:5","price":"5. அவளுடைய கழுத்தில் முறுக்கேறிய ஈச்சங்கயிறுதான். (அதனால் சுருக்கிடப்பட்டு அவளும் அழிந்து விடுவாள்.)","arabic":"فِي جِيدِهَا حَبۡلٞ مِّن مَّسَدِۭ","category":["111 (Al-Masad)","Al-Masad","Surah Al-Masad"],"ayahNumber":6221,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fī jīdihā ḥablun min masadin ","translations":["In","her neck","(will be) a rope","of","palm-fiber","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["fī","jīdihā","ḥablun","min","masadin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,470],[2,470,1530],[3,1530,3110],[4,3110,3670],[5,3670,6285]]}}],"chapter":["111 (Al-Masad)","Al-Masad","Surah Al-Masad","Chapter Al-Masad","Masad","Surah Masad","Chapter Masad","Al Masad","Surah Al Masad","Chapter Al Masad","Surah 111","Chapter 111","The Palm Fiber","المسد"],"version":{"key":"tamil_baqavi","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ta","version":"1.0.1","last_update":1609966800,"title":"Tamil Translation - Abdulhamid Albaqoi","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Tamil by Sh. Abdulhamid Albaqoi"}}